direction: down

title: "Zouroboros Architecture"

interface: |md
  ## Interface Layer
  - CLI (`orchestrate-v5`, `doctor`, `install`)
  - TUI dashboard
  - Hono API + SSE
  - Scheduled agents (5)
|
