execution: |md
  ## Execution & Intelligence
  - Executor registry: Claude Code, Gemini CLI, Codex CLI, Hermes Agent, Mimir Memory Sage
  - Transport factory: Bridge, ACP, Mimir
  - Adaptive routing: 6-signal core, budget/role-aware 8-signal path
  - RAG enrichment: Ollama embeddings + Qdrant (19 SDK KBs)
|
execution.style.fill: "#F3E8FF"
execution.style.stroke: "#CBD5E1"
execution.style.stroke-width: 2
execution.style.border-radius: 12

governance: |md
  ## Governance & Resilience
  - Pipeline gates: seed validation, post-flight eval, gap audit
  - Circuit breakers, cascade manager, stagnation detector
  - Budget governor
  - Context sharing
|
governance.style.fill: "#ECFCCB"
governance.style.stroke: "#CBD5E1"
governance.style.stroke-width: 2
governance.style.border-radius: 12

foundation: |md
  ## Foundation
  - Personas & role registry
  - Self-heal engine
  - Health Council: Healer, Doctor, Introspector, Steward (Mimir)
  - Heartbeat scheduler
|
foundation.style.fill: "#FFE4E6"
foundation.style.stroke: "#CBD5E1"
foundation.style.stroke-width: 2
foundation.style.border-radius: 12

mimir: |md
  **Mimir path**
  Memory system → memory gate → Mimir transport → downstream swarm tasks
|
mimir.style.fill: "#FEF3C7"
